WEBVTT

00:00:06.610 --> 00:00:13.647
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by
7️⃣Shooting Stars Team @Viki.com

00:00:13.647 --> 00:00:14.848
I did my best.

00:00:14.848 --> 00:00:16.950
You did? Well, I did my best, too.

00:00:16.950 --> 00:00:19.219
By the time I took over, it was too late.

00:00:19.219 --> 00:00:21.154
By the time you took over, it was too late?

00:00:21.154 --> 00:00:22.689
Please give me one more chance.

00:00:22.689 --> 00:00:23.826
- But who's going to give me another chance?
- You aren't suited for this industry.

00:00:23.826 --> 00:00:25.258
You aren't suited for this industry.

00:00:25.258 --> 00:00:26.659
He's incompetent beyond words.

00:00:26.659 --> 00:00:28.128
You're better off changing jobs.

00:00:28.128 --> 00:00:30.463
Maybe you should get a tutor.

00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:33.967
He's always absent for sketching classes.

00:00:33.967 --> 00:00:35.435
But it's better when he isn't around.

00:00:35.435 --> 00:00:37.070
I've cleared up your messes way too many times.

00:00:37.070 --> 00:00:38.104
What the heck are you trying to say?

00:00:38.104 --> 00:00:40.407
Let's work together to improve.

00:00:40.407 --> 00:00:42.074
He's so...

00:00:46.780 --> 00:00:48.814
1, 4, 2, 8, 5, 7...

00:01:35.911 --> 00:01:40.292
[Adapted from Zhong Min Rui's novel]

00:01:57.750 --> 00:02:00.220
All right, we've reached Starry Islet.

00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:01.955
Collect your luggage up ahead.

00:02:01.955 --> 00:02:04.591
What do we have most here?

00:02:04.591 --> 00:02:07.160
Turtles!

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:09.729
The shaved ice up the mountains
is delicious too.

00:02:09.729 --> 00:02:12.699
Many people come here
for diving and shaved ice.

00:02:12.699 --> 00:02:14.625
But what else is there to explore?

00:02:14.625 --> 00:02:17.475
Tons! So much more to explore!

00:02:19.839 --> 00:02:20.840
The ocean is one attraction,

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:23.409
but there's close to no light pollution
up the mountains at night.

00:02:23.409 --> 00:02:24.978
You can bike up the mountains

00:02:24.978 --> 00:02:27.975
and make a wish if you're lucky enough
to catch shooting stars.

00:02:29.883 --> 00:02:30.915
Hong!

00:02:30.915 --> 00:02:31.917
Hey, Hong!

00:02:31.917 --> 00:02:33.720
You know, I'm great with the guitar.

00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:34.687
[Ladder Steps]

00:02:34.687 --> 00:02:37.290
The fruits today are extra sweet.

00:02:37.290 --> 00:02:38.992
- The season really matters.
- Oh, you're all here.

00:02:38.992 --> 00:02:39.926
Village Chief.

00:02:39.926 --> 00:02:41.127
- The village chief is here!
- It's the village chief.

00:02:41.127 --> 00:02:42.623
- Perfect.
- Here, take one.

00:02:42.623 --> 00:02:45.478
Fresh out of the print! Grab one!

00:02:49.903 --> 00:02:51.771
- Village Chief, have some fruit.
- Okay, thanks.

00:02:51.771 --> 00:02:54.340
- I'll get you a fork.
- Oh, you're too nice.

00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:55.475
Hang on, I'll grab a fork.

00:02:55.475 --> 00:02:57.043
- Thank you.
- It's so sweet.

00:02:57.043 --> 00:02:58.111
Wan Zhe!

00:02:58.111 --> 00:02:59.245
You're out of bed?

00:02:59.245 --> 00:03:00.246
Li Wan Zhe!

00:03:00.246 --> 00:03:01.948
What took you so long?

00:03:01.948 --> 00:03:03.049
Violence in the morning?

00:03:03.049 --> 00:03:04.976
You'll ruin your image.

00:03:06.653 --> 00:03:08.621
Hama-chan! Morning!

00:03:09.322 --> 00:03:11.756
Shaved ice in the morning
will ruin your stomach.

00:03:11.756 --> 00:03:13.526
But I just love it.

00:03:13.526 --> 00:03:15.027
Suit yourself.

00:03:16.994 --> 00:03:19.466
Deliver five bowls of shaved ice for me later.

00:03:19.466 --> 00:03:21.434
- To the port.
- Got it.

00:03:21.434 --> 00:03:22.502
When you're on the main island,

00:03:22.502 --> 00:03:23.636
help me make a trip to the fishing harbor

00:03:23.636 --> 00:03:25.917
and buy some turtle egg cakes.

00:03:31.778 --> 00:03:33.913
One, two, three, four.

00:03:37.984 --> 00:03:39.618
Work time!

00:03:47.927 --> 00:03:48.927
Xiang Yong!

00:03:48.927 --> 00:03:50.230
Xiang Yong, why are you back?

00:03:50.230 --> 00:03:51.996
I really missed you.

00:03:51.996 --> 00:03:53.099
Dad.

00:03:53.099 --> 00:03:54.367
Old man.

00:03:54.367 --> 00:03:56.368
My idol is back.

00:03:58.605 --> 00:03:59.906
Xiang Yong.

00:03:59.906 --> 00:04:01.174
Here, watermelon candy.

00:04:01.174 --> 00:04:03.030
It's your favorite.

00:04:06.613 --> 00:04:08.147
Thanks, Hong.

00:04:08.147 --> 00:04:10.250
But I don't like them anymore.

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:11.784
Well...

00:04:11.784 --> 00:04:13.853
What about turtles and drawing?

00:04:13.853 --> 00:04:14.953
Do you still like those?

00:04:14.953 --> 00:04:17.357
Xiang Yong! Xiang Yong!

00:04:17.357 --> 00:04:19.259
- De.
- You haven't been back in ages!

00:04:19.259 --> 00:04:21.594
Didn't you have an exhibition abroad?

00:04:21.594 --> 00:04:23.663
- Nah.
- Xiang Yong! Come here!

00:04:23.663 --> 00:04:25.198
Come on in, let's catch up.

00:04:25.198 --> 00:04:26.231
Okay, I'll chat with you next time.

00:04:26.231 --> 00:04:27.400
Xiang Yong's a busy man.

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:28.801
- Don't bother him.
- I'll head back first. Thanks.

00:04:28.801 --> 00:04:30.670
- Hey, it's my chance to grab my dream.
- You sure you don't want any?

00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:31.738
Don't stop me.

00:04:31.738 --> 00:04:33.206
Grab what? Don't be ridiculous.

00:04:33.206 --> 00:04:35.441
- Don't you know who he is?
- You'll help me leave the island, right?

00:04:35.441 --> 00:04:37.043
No way. Get to work.

00:04:37.043 --> 00:04:38.838
I need money for the boat fare.

00:04:42.382 --> 00:04:43.082
- Village Chief!
- You're superb.

00:04:43.082 --> 00:04:45.752
- You'll get all five votes from my family.
- Make sure you keep your word.

00:04:45.752 --> 00:04:46.953
When I'm the village chief,

00:04:46.953 --> 00:04:48.154
the roads become so clean.

00:04:48.154 --> 00:04:49.222
The drains are sparkling too.

00:04:49.222 --> 00:04:50.456
- I'll vote for you.
- Isn't that Xiang Yong?

00:04:50.456 --> 00:04:51.491
Xiang Yong!

00:04:51.491 --> 00:04:53.426
- Xiang Yong's back!
- It's Xiang Yong!

00:04:53.426 --> 00:04:54.560
Xiang Yong!

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:56.663
- It's rare for him to be back!
- Oh, you're back!

00:04:56.663 --> 00:04:58.197
Xiang Yong, is this a special visit?

00:04:58.197 --> 00:05:00.133
- Xiang Yong!
- Did you publish a book?

00:05:00.133 --> 00:05:01.701
He's the one with the art exhibition.

00:05:01.701 --> 00:05:02.535
Yeah, we even went to see.

00:05:02.535 --> 00:05:03.836
- I didn't have an art exhibition.
- You did!

00:05:03.836 --> 00:05:05.905
I told my younger bro to look up to you.

00:05:05.905 --> 00:05:08.435
You're so amazing.

00:05:09.575 --> 00:05:10.743
Let's take photos, come on.

00:05:10.743 --> 00:05:13.012
Starry Islet's greatest artist. That's him.

00:05:13.012 --> 00:05:14.914
I watched him grow up.

00:05:14.914 --> 00:05:16.082
- He Xiang Yong.
- Be careful.

00:05:16.082 --> 00:05:18.915
- Get over here.
- Watch out for traffic.

00:05:33.533 --> 00:05:35.167
Thanks.

00:05:35.835 --> 00:05:37.003
Oh, please.

00:05:37.003 --> 00:05:38.805
We've known each other for ages.

00:05:38.805 --> 00:05:41.274
Our chemistry is god tier.

00:05:41.274 --> 00:05:43.276
You know how the islanders are.

00:05:43.276 --> 00:05:44.744
They have too much time on their hands.

00:05:44.744 --> 00:05:46.779
All they do is gossip.

00:05:46.779 --> 00:05:48.381
But it can't be helped.

00:05:48.381 --> 00:05:51.307
Blame yourself for being
the star of Starry Islet.

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:57.490
I was planning to grab
shaved ice and jelly with you.

00:05:57.490 --> 00:06:00.159
It's fine. I'm bring some over for you.

00:06:02.328 --> 00:06:03.896
Why the sudden visit?

00:06:03.896 --> 00:06:05.931
You didn't even tell me.

00:06:08.334 --> 00:06:09.469
You said it, a sudden visit it is.

00:06:09.469 --> 00:06:11.704
No notices needed.

00:06:11.704 --> 00:06:13.505
True.

00:06:14.907 --> 00:06:17.643
I bet you just missed me.

00:06:17.643 --> 00:06:18.778
You know?

00:06:18.778 --> 00:06:20.380
While you were away,

00:06:20.380 --> 00:06:22.281
my mom was super annoying.

00:06:22.281 --> 00:06:24.350
She always gushes about how great you are.

00:06:24.350 --> 00:06:26.185
You leave the island for your dreams.

00:06:26.185 --> 00:06:29.222
And then she nags at me
for being a useless shut-in gamer.

00:06:29.222 --> 00:06:31.290
She wants me to learn from you.

00:06:31.290 --> 00:06:33.126
My ears are dropping off from her nagging.

00:06:33.126 --> 00:06:34.827
And Village Chief Wang!

00:06:34.827 --> 00:06:35.995
He plans to build a resort.

00:06:35.995 --> 00:06:37.296
One that's solar powered!

00:06:37.296 --> 00:06:40.996
I seriously think he's aiming to be the mayor.

00:06:49.275 --> 00:06:50.776
We're here.

00:06:58.718 --> 00:07:00.486
Mr. He.

00:07:00.486 --> 00:07:01.654
Mr. He!

00:07:01.654 --> 00:07:04.090
Du Du, have you seen Mr. He?

00:07:04.090 --> 00:07:05.691
Where's everyone?

00:07:18.471 --> 00:07:20.572
Mr. He.

00:07:21.174 --> 00:07:23.998
Your dear Xiang Yong is back.

00:07:24.777 --> 00:07:27.013
I know.

00:07:27.013 --> 00:07:29.742
Your mom blasted it into the group chat.

00:07:51.604 --> 00:07:53.739
Mom.

00:07:53.739 --> 00:07:55.568
I'm back.

00:08:02.382 --> 00:08:03.382
Are you hungry?

00:08:03.382 --> 00:08:04.382
I'll cook you some noodles.

00:08:04.382 --> 00:08:05.966
Okay.

00:08:09.355 --> 00:08:10.990
I'm not hungry.

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:16.195
Where did this crap piece of wood come from?

00:08:16.195 --> 00:08:18.564
Why bring it back if you don't need it?

00:08:18.564 --> 00:08:20.266
Please, keep the storage baskets and broom.

00:08:20.266 --> 00:08:22.501
No one runs an inn like this.

00:08:23.469 --> 00:08:25.337
And you're drinking so early in the morning.

00:08:28.941 --> 00:08:30.009
Good lord.

00:08:30.009 --> 00:08:32.011
You barely come back once a year.

00:08:32.011 --> 00:08:35.248
Now you're back, you give me an attitude.

00:08:35.248 --> 00:08:38.918
If you don't want to be here, don't come back.

00:08:38.918 --> 00:08:40.653
That's not true, Mr. He.

00:08:40.653 --> 00:08:42.889
He's just tired from work.

00:08:42.889 --> 00:08:44.924
I bet he's also seasick from
the gusting wind this morning.

00:08:44.924 --> 00:08:45.925
He doesn't mean it.

00:08:45.925 --> 00:08:47.760
Oh, poor thing. He's tired?

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:49.829
- Are you tired from work?
- Yeah.

00:08:49.829 --> 00:08:51.831
I'm tired. Du Du's tired, too.

00:08:51.831 --> 00:08:53.099
Everyone's tired.

00:08:53.099 --> 00:08:55.001
Work gets to everyone.

00:08:55.001 --> 00:08:56.869
It isn't even a rest day.

00:08:56.869 --> 00:08:58.070
He comes back on a regular day,

00:08:58.070 --> 00:08:59.272
and he complains about being tired?

00:08:59.272 --> 00:09:01.040
Listen up.

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:02.675
I also run a business.

00:09:02.675 --> 00:09:04.110
If I find myself an employee

00:09:04.110 --> 00:09:05.678
as lazy and useless as him,

00:09:05.678 --> 00:09:06.812
that'll be a lifetime of bad luck.

00:09:06.812 --> 00:09:07.914
He wants the best of everything.

00:09:07.914 --> 00:09:09.281
Yes.

00:09:10.249 --> 00:09:12.118
I'm lazy and useless.

00:09:12.118 --> 00:09:14.921
If you're irked by the sight of me, don't look.

00:09:14.921 --> 00:09:16.522
Just ignore the fact that I'm back.

00:09:16.522 --> 00:09:17.657
I didn't ask you to come back.

00:09:17.657 --> 00:09:19.158
You're the one who ditched work to come back.

00:09:19.158 --> 00:09:20.459
Now, you're even giving me an attitude.

00:09:20.459 --> 00:09:21.527
You scold me for not coming back.

00:09:21.527 --> 00:09:22.562
Now that I'm back, you still snap at me.

00:09:22.562 --> 00:09:24.297
This glum face comes from your genes.

00:09:24.297 --> 00:09:25.998
- Hey.
- You always act like this when I'm back.

00:09:25.998 --> 00:09:28.534
All right. Stop.

00:09:28.534 --> 00:09:30.136
1 minute, 10.9 seconds.

00:09:30.136 --> 00:09:33.399
Congratulations on breaking
your previous fight record.

00:09:33.399 --> 00:09:35.033
Congratulations, truly.

00:09:36.576 --> 00:09:38.544
All right, don't be mad.

00:09:42.515 --> 00:09:44.016
Come on.

00:09:44.016 --> 00:09:45.151
Calm down.

00:09:45.151 --> 00:09:47.019
Drink up, Mr. He.

00:09:47.019 --> 00:09:48.654
Cheers.

00:09:48.654 --> 00:09:50.756
Cheers? Screw off.

00:10:05.237 --> 00:10:07.340
Do you have a lot of time to spare?

00:10:07.340 --> 00:10:09.007
Don't you have a shop to tend?

00:10:11.978 --> 00:10:13.045
Nah.

00:10:13.045 --> 00:10:14.647
My mom has a message for you.

00:10:14.647 --> 00:10:16.616
The village chief is hosting a dinner.

00:10:16.616 --> 00:10:17.817
He Xiang Yong happens to be back, too.

00:10:17.817 --> 00:10:19.518
He's invited you over. You must go.

00:10:21.554 --> 00:10:24.223
Mr. He, I'll get back to work.

00:10:29.829 --> 00:10:31.196
Sorry.

00:10:33.265 --> 00:10:34.967
The chair.

00:10:38.938 --> 00:10:40.673
Thanks.

00:10:40.673 --> 00:10:43.509
He Xiang Yong, make sure you come tonight.

00:10:52.852 --> 00:10:53.886
Come on.

00:10:53.886 --> 00:10:55.121
Bottoms up.

00:10:55.121 --> 00:10:56.455
Thanks.

00:10:56.455 --> 00:10:58.658
You've seen me serve everyone, yeah?

00:10:58.658 --> 00:11:00.426
You get it, right?

00:11:00.426 --> 00:11:03.062
You have to pick me, yeah?

00:11:03.062 --> 00:11:05.798
- All right?
- We will.

00:11:05.798 --> 00:11:07.366
Please, I'm counting on you.

00:11:07.366 --> 00:11:09.735
Enjoy the food. Take your time.

00:11:09.735 --> 00:11:11.865
This tastes amazing.

00:11:12.538 --> 00:11:13.539
Eat your fill.

00:11:13.539 --> 00:11:15.307
Eat up.

00:11:15.307 --> 00:11:17.009
Dig in.

00:11:17.009 --> 00:11:20.012
Let me see... No, not this one.

00:11:20.012 --> 00:11:21.147
I want this song.

00:11:21.147 --> 00:11:23.215
24206.

00:11:23.215 --> 00:11:25.284
- 78257.
- Okay, I'll put it in for you.

00:11:25.284 --> 00:11:26.352
Not yet!

00:11:26.352 --> 00:11:28.287
27394. Thanks.

00:11:28.287 --> 00:11:29.288
Remember, vote for me.

00:11:29.288 --> 00:11:30.622
Thanks.

00:11:32.692 --> 00:11:37.430
Mr. He, when is your son going to the U.S.?

00:11:37.430 --> 00:11:40.132
How about an art exhibition in Europe?

00:11:40.132 --> 00:11:41.734
Luzhou's quicker.

00:11:41.734 --> 00:11:43.269
What? Here, drink up.

00:11:43.269 --> 00:11:45.404
What does he draw?

00:11:45.404 --> 00:11:46.839
I have no clue.

00:11:46.839 --> 00:11:49.575
- Eat your fill.
- Here, Xiang Yong. Have more.

00:11:49.575 --> 00:11:51.711
- I didn't see you eat much.
- Hey, He.

00:11:51.711 --> 00:11:54.213
Isn't your little assistant joining us?

00:11:54.213 --> 00:11:55.614
He's having a day off.

00:11:55.614 --> 00:11:57.661
Who knows where he went since the morning.

00:11:59.285 --> 00:12:01.554
When did we get a new hire?

00:12:01.554 --> 00:12:04.090
He's been here for some time.

00:12:04.090 --> 00:12:06.826
And he's ultra handsome.

00:12:06.826 --> 00:12:08.828
A total hottie.

00:12:08.828 --> 00:12:10.563
- Right?
- Not bad, I guess.

00:12:10.563 --> 00:12:14.510
He managed to survive
past three days in my household?

00:12:15.201 --> 00:12:17.503
Don't be rude. He has a great personality.

00:12:17.503 --> 00:12:19.038
Gets along perfectly with me.

00:12:19.038 --> 00:12:20.072
Not the slightest bit like you.

00:12:20.072 --> 00:12:22.275
Impossible to talk to with a shit attitude.

00:12:22.275 --> 00:12:24.243
- What shit attitude?
- Just like right now.

00:12:24.243 --> 00:12:25.578
Yeah, you're so nice.

00:12:25.578 --> 00:12:26.846
Come on, eat. Don't fight.

00:12:26.846 --> 00:12:28.214
- Okay.
- Yeah.

00:12:28.214 --> 00:12:29.348
- Come on.
- Here.

00:12:29.348 --> 00:12:30.483
Listen to the doctor.

00:12:30.483 --> 00:12:32.084
Shut your mouth if you only talk crap.

00:12:32.084 --> 00:12:33.986
Drink up. Cheers.

00:12:33.986 --> 00:12:35.821
Come on, bottoms up.

00:12:35.821 --> 00:12:37.522
Drink.

00:12:40.025 --> 00:12:41.526
Village Chief Wang.

00:12:42.228 --> 00:12:44.363
Let's sing together.

00:12:44.363 --> 00:12:45.564
You go ahead.

00:12:45.564 --> 00:12:47.967
Sing with me. This is a great song.

00:12:47.967 --> 00:12:49.983
Everyone knows me for this song.

00:12:55.913 --> 00:12:57.748
What? Aren't you eating?

00:12:59.879 --> 00:13:00.946
It's too hot.

00:13:00.946 --> 00:13:02.214
I lost my appetite.

00:13:02.214 --> 00:13:03.883
Lost your appetite?

00:13:03.883 --> 00:13:04.917
Don't try to fool me.

00:13:04.917 --> 00:13:06.652
Your dad's the real reason.

00:13:08.754 --> 00:13:10.022
If your mom said the same thing to you,

00:13:10.022 --> 00:13:11.557
would you still feel happy?

00:13:11.557 --> 00:13:12.625
I'll be fine.

00:13:12.625 --> 00:13:14.192
Doesn't bother me.

00:13:16.795 --> 00:13:18.329
Wan Zhe.

00:13:19.865 --> 00:13:21.533
Long time no see.

00:13:23.369 --> 00:13:25.103
Want to have a bite?

00:13:28.741 --> 00:13:30.442
Fine.

00:13:31.210 --> 00:13:32.912
When we're back, help me clear a stage.

00:13:32.912 --> 00:13:35.247
Don't touch my snacks stash.

00:13:35.247 --> 00:13:36.649
I'll think about it.

00:13:36.649 --> 00:13:38.116
Think about it?

00:13:38.884 --> 00:13:40.652
No, hands off my stash.

00:13:43.088 --> 00:13:44.791
You want to study in Japan?

00:13:44.791 --> 00:13:45.823
Nah.

00:13:45.823 --> 00:13:46.992
You want to travel there?

00:13:46.992 --> 00:13:47.993
I'm broke.

00:13:47.993 --> 00:13:49.995
But why are you on such great terms with Hai?

00:13:49.995 --> 00:13:52.698
He's so aloof and barely talks.

00:13:52.698 --> 00:13:54.200
We get along because he talks little.

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.768
Keeps my ears at peace.

00:13:55.768 --> 00:13:56.768
Look at my mom.

00:13:56.768 --> 00:13:58.303
One of her is enough.

00:13:59.171 --> 00:14:00.539
I'm going to sing. Singing time.

00:14:00.539 --> 00:14:02.441
What song?

00:14:02.441 --> 00:14:04.343
Come on, what's your pick?

00:14:04.343 --> 00:14:06.445
An English song?

00:14:06.445 --> 00:14:09.520
You didn't tell me how long you'll be here.

00:14:11.183 --> 00:14:14.553
I guess... for a while.

00:14:14.553 --> 00:14:15.855
What does that mean?

00:14:15.855 --> 00:14:18.424
Are you using up your annual leave?

00:14:18.424 --> 00:14:20.359
I don't have that now.

00:14:20.359 --> 00:14:22.494
You don't have annual leave?

00:14:22.494 --> 00:14:23.562
Did you take special days off?

00:14:23.562 --> 00:14:24.864
Nah.

00:14:24.864 --> 00:14:26.283
What then?

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:29.390
I'm unemployed.

00:14:30.302 --> 00:14:32.048
Can't hear you!

00:14:33.505 --> 00:14:34.740
I've been fired!

00:14:34.740 --> 00:14:36.430
One song.

00:14:43.782 --> 00:14:46.185
I think a Taiwanese song is better.

00:14:46.185 --> 00:14:47.186
A Taiwanese song?

00:14:47.186 --> 00:14:48.888
I think I'll just sing a Taiwanese song too.

00:14:48.888 --> 00:14:51.257
Chen Lei's song? Let me pick it.

00:14:51.257 --> 00:14:52.324
All right?

00:14:52.324 --> 00:14:53.425
- Let's all sing together.
- Eat up.

00:14:53.425 --> 00:14:54.660
Come on, sing and drink.

00:14:54.660 --> 00:14:56.228
Start singing!

00:14:56.228 --> 00:14:57.630
I'll pick Chen Lei's song.

00:14:57.630 --> 00:14:59.498
Choose whatever you like.

00:15:00.633 --> 00:15:02.550
He Xiang Yong.

00:15:04.524 --> 00:15:06.972
Drink up. Come on.

00:15:06.972 --> 00:15:08.306
Cheers.

00:15:09.808 --> 00:15:11.481
It's fine.

00:15:49.574 --> 00:15:51.162
[turnyoung_ho]
[_how.hello_ commented on your story.]

00:15:54.855 --> 00:15:56.550
[_how.hello_]
[Chen Hao Wei]

00:16:02.528 --> 00:16:05.030
I don't see the disciplinary master.

00:16:05.030 --> 00:16:08.099
Happy birthday to you!

00:16:15.407 --> 00:16:16.842
Thank goodness I'm smart.

00:16:16.842 --> 00:16:18.510
I figured you'd be here.

00:16:22.514 --> 00:16:23.515
Look.

00:16:23.515 --> 00:16:25.350
There are so many shooting stars tonight.

00:16:32.591 --> 00:16:34.226
I really miss this.

00:16:34.226 --> 00:16:35.527
Do you still remember?

00:16:35.527 --> 00:16:37.296
We used to come here all the time
as kids to make wishes.

00:16:37.296 --> 00:16:39.598
You always wished to become an artist.

00:16:39.598 --> 00:16:41.533
You know, I really admire you.

00:16:43.836 --> 00:16:45.670
In what sense?

00:16:47.339 --> 00:16:49.574
I'm not an artist.

00:16:50.743 --> 00:16:53.345
I'm not even worthy of picking up a brush.

00:16:54.079 --> 00:16:58.617
Everyone keeps talking about Europe and France.

00:16:58.617 --> 00:17:00.686
What a joke.

00:17:00.686 --> 00:17:03.789
I got myself fired as an editor.

00:17:03.789 --> 00:17:05.290
I even owe...

00:17:11.296 --> 00:17:14.099
Anyway, my crap life isn't worth envying.

00:17:14.099 --> 00:17:16.001
I've had enough.

00:17:16.702 --> 00:17:20.105
I really hope I can stop being He Xiang Yong.

00:17:20.105 --> 00:17:21.507
Hey, you've been talking so quietly.

00:17:21.507 --> 00:17:23.308
Can't you speak up?

00:17:24.109 --> 00:17:25.210
I said!

00:17:25.210 --> 00:17:28.013
I hope I can stop being He Xiang Yong!

00:17:28.013 --> 00:17:29.047
That's easy.

00:17:29.047 --> 00:17:30.482
Dive into the sea.

00:17:33.185 --> 00:17:34.720
- Great idea.
- Really?

00:17:34.720 --> 00:17:36.510
Come on then. Let's do it together.

00:17:36.510 --> 00:17:38.624
- Dive into the sea!
- How about this spot?

00:17:38.624 --> 00:17:41.193
Wait, I was kidding.

00:17:41.193 --> 00:17:42.861
I wasn't. Come on, let's jump down.

00:17:42.861 --> 00:17:44.329
I was really kidding. Sorry, I didn't mean...

00:17:44.329 --> 00:17:46.089
I'll jump down and restart my life.

00:17:46.089 --> 00:17:47.991
I was just kidding!

00:17:55.474 --> 00:17:56.975
If I...

00:17:56.975 --> 00:17:59.411
If I hadn't known you for over two decades,

00:17:59.411 --> 00:18:01.680
I would shove you down right away.

00:18:02.848 --> 00:18:04.749
I'll get it back for you.

00:18:28.140 --> 00:18:30.209
- Mr. Hua.
- You're back.

00:18:30.209 --> 00:18:32.064
Haven't you gone home?

00:18:33.512 --> 00:18:34.946
Goodnight.

00:18:36.482 --> 00:18:38.584
Xiang Yong.

00:18:38.584 --> 00:18:40.752
I'm cooking for you.

00:18:40.752 --> 00:18:43.254
Your dad was worried
you didn't have enough for dinner.

00:18:44.223 --> 00:18:45.257
He's clearly drunk.

00:18:45.257 --> 00:18:47.726
But he insisted on cooking
garlic prawn flat noodles for you.

00:18:47.726 --> 00:18:49.461
I was scared he'd blow the kitchen up.

00:18:49.461 --> 00:18:52.030
So, I told him to sleep
and leave the cooking to me.

00:18:52.030 --> 00:18:54.479
Make sure you take a bite or two.

00:18:55.701 --> 00:18:56.969
Thanks, Mr. Hua.

00:18:56.969 --> 00:18:58.370
Give me a second.

00:18:59.638 --> 00:19:01.272
My flat noodles!

00:19:04.743 --> 00:19:07.579
Darn brat.

00:19:07.579 --> 00:19:09.581
Don't ever come back.

00:19:16.421 --> 00:19:18.990
I can't guarantee it'll taste good.

00:19:34.473 --> 00:19:36.241
What's the matter?

00:19:36.241 --> 00:19:38.611
Not enough garlic?

00:19:38.611 --> 00:19:39.611
I'll cook another bowl...

00:19:39.611 --> 00:19:41.613
No, that's not it.

00:19:41.613 --> 00:19:43.148
It's delicious.

00:19:44.850 --> 00:19:47.653
But why are you munching it down so grumpily?

00:19:47.653 --> 00:19:49.354
Bad mood?

00:19:50.889 --> 00:19:55.694
I just thought about when I was younger.

00:19:55.694 --> 00:19:58.430
Whenever my family had a celebration,

00:19:58.430 --> 00:20:01.200
Dad would cook these noodles for me.

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:03.001
But today...

00:20:04.870 --> 00:20:06.415
Mr. Hua...

00:20:07.874 --> 00:20:10.341
Have I disappointed my dad?

00:20:11.476 --> 00:20:14.913
Xiang Yong, you're a young man out in society.

00:20:14.913 --> 00:20:17.516
Things are bound to get rough.

00:20:17.516 --> 00:20:20.419
You can't expect everything to go your way.

00:20:20.419 --> 00:20:21.920
When I used to work in a big hospital,

00:20:21.920 --> 00:20:23.555
things were the same for me.

00:20:24.156 --> 00:20:27.926
Obstacles are what helps us grow.

00:20:30.095 --> 00:20:31.796
But...

00:20:34.533 --> 00:20:40.438
Anyway, I think I'm really useless right now.

00:20:42.474 --> 00:20:44.543
That depends on what you're aiming for.

00:20:44.543 --> 00:20:48.213
Do you want to be useful or fawned over?

00:20:48.914 --> 00:20:52.817
Or are you happy with just loving yourself?

00:20:53.518 --> 00:20:57.155
It's easy for parents to be content.

00:20:57.155 --> 00:20:58.590
As long as their children are doing fine,

00:20:58.590 --> 00:21:00.993
they have nothing more to ask for.

00:21:00.993 --> 00:21:02.527
So, here's the thing.

00:21:03.128 --> 00:21:06.564
Don't take your dad's harsh words to heart.

00:21:08.600 --> 00:21:11.469
He's really glad you're back.

00:21:13.071 --> 00:21:14.973
Really?

00:21:14.973 --> 00:21:17.242
He's happy?

00:21:17.242 --> 00:21:18.744
Don't use your eyes.

00:21:18.744 --> 00:21:20.879
Use your heart to feel.

00:21:22.581 --> 00:21:24.382
Hear me out.

00:21:25.017 --> 00:21:28.720
Find a chance to have a good chat with him.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:33.825
At times, giving in first doesn't mean losing.

00:21:35.594 --> 00:21:41.466
But you know how we can't have a long chat.

00:21:41.466 --> 00:21:44.102
Don't be in a hurry. Take your time.

00:21:44.770 --> 00:21:48.440
Not everything that happens is bad.

00:21:48.440 --> 00:21:49.508
Look at it from a different perspective.

00:21:49.508 --> 00:21:51.076
Perhaps...

00:21:51.076 --> 00:21:52.811
Perhaps the heavens are giving you a chance

00:21:52.811 --> 00:21:54.646
to make a change.

00:21:54.646 --> 00:21:56.942
It all depends on whether you grab it.

00:21:58.150 --> 00:22:01.720
All right, eat up before the food gets cold.

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:04.622
Regardless of what happens,
you can count on me.

00:22:05.891 --> 00:22:07.559
Thanks, Mr. Hua.

00:22:08.293 --> 00:22:11.163
Hey, you sure you don't want more garlic.

00:22:11.163 --> 00:22:12.964
- Nah, I'm good.
- Are you sure?

00:22:12.964 --> 00:22:15.167
I'll get some chilli.

00:22:15.167 --> 00:22:16.467
All right.

00:22:34.086 --> 00:22:35.287
Why isn't he back yet?

00:22:35.287 --> 00:22:37.055
It's already so late.

00:22:50.641 --> 00:22:51.966
[Beautiful Homeland Competition]
[Special Award for He Xiang Yong]

00:22:51.966 --> 00:22:54.330
[Starry Islet Tin Man Award]
[Third Prize: He Xiang Yong]

00:23:25.203 --> 00:23:28.039
Who said things get better when we grow up?

00:23:31.276 --> 00:23:33.411
Bullshit.

00:23:34.479 --> 00:23:37.048
It sucks now that I've grown up.

00:23:38.683 --> 00:23:40.585
Utter crap.

00:24:27.399 --> 00:24:29.100
Who's there?

00:25:18.139 --> 00:25:20.020
[He Xiang Yong]

00:25:25.724 --> 00:25:28.860
It's easy for parents to be content.

00:25:28.860 --> 00:25:30.362
As long as their children are doing fine,

00:25:30.362 --> 00:25:32.263
they have nothing more to ask for.

00:25:38.937 --> 00:25:41.839
Damn. Why is it so freaking heavy?

00:25:41.839 --> 00:25:42.840
So damn heavy.

00:25:42.840 --> 00:25:44.209
Hey, come and help me.

00:25:44.209 --> 00:25:46.005
Chen Hao Wei!

00:25:46.745 --> 00:25:48.453
Coming!

00:26:11.436 --> 00:26:14.228
Hello, I'm Chen Hao Wei from Class 2.

00:26:15.540 --> 00:26:16.474
From that day...

00:26:16.474 --> 00:26:17.929
He Xiang Yong!

00:26:17.929 --> 00:26:19.477
I made up my mind.

00:26:19.477 --> 00:26:21.112
- He Xiang Yong!
- This name...

00:26:21.112 --> 00:26:23.682
It no longer had anything to do with me.

00:26:23.682 --> 00:26:24.783
Chen Hao Wei, stop bothering me.

00:26:24.783 --> 00:26:27.118
I didn't want to mention it again.

00:26:29.220 --> 00:26:33.620
That was until we met once more.

00:26:33.620 --> 00:26:41.588
[Epilogue]

00:27:00.552 --> 00:27:02.287
Hey, the disciplinary master's here.
Aren't you leaving?

00:27:02.287 --> 00:27:03.121
The disciplinary master is here?

00:27:03.121 --> 00:27:04.189
He's here. Right up there.

00:27:04.189 --> 00:27:05.890
- Come on.
- What are you doing?

00:27:05.890 --> 00:27:07.492
What the heck are you doing?

00:27:07.492 --> 00:27:08.994
I don't see the disciplinary master!

00:27:08.994 --> 00:27:11.196
Stop running!

00:27:11.196 --> 00:27:12.397
He's right behind us.

00:27:12.397 --> 00:27:13.465
Where is he?

00:27:13.465 --> 00:27:14.833
Behind us.

00:27:14.833 --> 00:27:16.067
Hang on, stop.

00:27:16.067 --> 00:27:17.568
Just move.

00:27:28.146 --> 00:27:29.947
Stop right there!

00:28:01.946 --> 00:28:03.114
Chen Hao Wei!

00:28:03.114 --> 00:28:04.416
He's the new hire?

00:28:04.416 --> 00:28:06.051
Why can't I say my name?

00:28:06.051 --> 00:28:07.285
- You don't recognize him?
- Who is he?

00:28:07.285 --> 00:28:08.921
- None of you know him?
- Yeah, we don't.

00:28:08.921 --> 00:28:09.921
The shooting stars!

00:28:09.921 --> 00:28:11.289
Didn't you make a wish, too?

00:28:11.289 --> 00:28:12.457
Why are you fine?

00:28:12.457 --> 00:28:14.025
The wish doesn't affect me.

00:28:14.025 --> 00:28:15.060
Li Wan Zhe!

00:28:15.060 --> 00:28:17.195
I like you!

00:28:17.195 --> 00:28:18.529
What?

00:28:19.330 --> 00:28:21.232
Have we met somewhere?